data.name: Dead Rails [Alpha]
data.description:
In 1899, a mysterious virus swept the American continent. Dubbed the "Zombie Plague", a cure was discovered in Mexico. Climb aboard your train and traverse the unforgiving, zombie-infested desert on your way to the cure...

Like and favorite the game for updates

Latest Update (3/28/2025) 

New POI - Town of Sterling, an abandoned town with a mineshaft full of secrets...
Nightmare Mode - After winning 1 normal game, you unlock nightmare mode with less loot, no passive regeneration, enemies do more damage + have more health, and you get more bonds upon completion.
Ores - Gold & Silver ores now spawn along the track and can be mined to get ore nuggets. (The miner class can mine these fast!)
Rotate Objects - You can now rotate objects in all 3 axis while dragging
Horse Cart - Spawns in farms, can be attached to a horse and allows items to be welded to it
New Zombie Variants - Zombies have a 5% chance of being 1 of 3 special v

data.name: 🎮Evade🎮
data.description:
Classic Roblox items are now visible in the shop! Play on the limited-time Roblox themed maps for special nextbots!

Steal Lupen the Leprechaun's golden coins, and use them to purchase limited time themed skins!

Action parkour game, where movement is the key to success in surviving the Nextbots.

⚠️Using exploits, fastflags, or any other forms of cheats will result in an unappealable ban ⚠️

⚠️ You may experience flashing lights and loud sounds in game
🛠️ Expect various updates in the coming months.
❓ To play, join Evade and press the 'Play' button. To exit, press [M] or click on the 'Menu' button while in game.

[E] - Interact
[G] - Emote
[1/2/3/F] - Equip item
[C/Ctrl] - Crouch
[T] - Whistle
[M] - Menu
[N] - VIP Menu

Inspired by Garry's Mod

data.name: Escape Baby Bobby Daycare! (FIRST PERSON OBBY)
data.description:
Are you ready to jump into Baby Bobby's Daycare? Let's get to it! This daycare isn't like the others, it is patrolled by a GIANT BABY and has some of the world's best security technology designed to stop you from escaping! Make your way through jumps, chases, liquid hot "MAGMA", and defeat Baby Bobby in an epic boss battle. Let's do this!

If you have fun please thumbs-up 👍 and favorite ⭐ to support the game. Thank you so much for playing!

Premium players get a free speed coil to use in game!

If you're stuck on a stage make sure to check out some of the fun power-ups in the shop, any purchases are greatly appreciated and support me in making future games but don't feel pressured, simply playing the game is just as meaningful to me as a developer ❤️. Have fun!

Join the Decent Obbies group so you don't miss out on future obby / parkour games!

data.name: Break In (Story)
data.description:
Move in day! There are white brick balconies, an absence of drapes, nostalgic pictures lining the walls and the smell of new house. A wooden staircase leads upstairs where 12 beds wait lamely for occupants.
 
The night may be stormy, but there are 11 unfamiliar players for you to meet, and a house full of secrets waiting to be discovered. 

Oh, and the murderers. I almost forgot to mention the murderers.

Sincerely, your fren
Cracky4

data.name: Carry A Friend! [2 Player Obby]
data.description:
Welcome to Carry A Friend [2 Player Obby]! 

Help your friend help you - carry, throw or pickup your friend and press different buttons to access different areas and progress in each obby. There are many 2 player obby puzzles and levels to choose from! Train your parkour abilities and reach the final level! 

💡How To Play: 
- Press E on a player to pair up with them! 👥
- Press E to pickup or throw your friend! 👤 
- Press the buttons ⬛ 
- Progress and don't leave anyone behind 🏆 
- Reach the END of the levels 🎌 
- Get in the Top Leaderboards 🌐 

Tags: Colorful, Super, Speed, Fun, Obby, Parkour, Teamwork, Run, Victory, Win, Faster, Platformer, Clicker, Easy 

Inspired by Teamwork Puzzles

data.name: Delivery Industry
data.description:
Welcome to Delivery Industry, 

Get ready for a wild ride in our epic truck simulator. You'll explore a huge, dynamic world, from the hustle and bustle of busy highways to the tranquility of scenic country roads. 

Our game brings you ultra-realistic map and awesome tractor units that make every journey thrilling. Choose your path in the trucking world. Join a big-time company or hit the road as an independent trucker. Each choice brings new adventures and challenges. Join our Roblox community for cool tips, fun ideas, and exclusive sneak peeks of what’s coming up.

data.name: Slap Battles👏
data.description: A game about slapping people into oblivion using different gloves with unique abilities. This game is very chaotic, so don't be surprised if you spot someone complaining about some hand that I'm pretty sure originated from hell itself. You earn slaps when slapping people, which are used to unlock new gloves. Gloves have abilities, some are passive, others are activated by pressing "E" (mobile players have a button). Shift lock is recommended. ANY FORM OF EXPLOITING WILL RESULT IN A PERMANENT BAN - don't risk it 😡😡😡😡😡😡 Credit to DM DOKU, Desolo Zantas and Tim Haywood for creating several songs used.

data.name: Shadow Boxing Battles
data.description:
This game is based off the trending Shadow Boxing game. Testing JUST STARTED! Will work on more features!
Please DM me if you have suggestions or if you find bugs!

⬆ ⬅ ➡ ⬇
HOW TO PLAY: The goal is to make your opponent look in the same direction that you move, which could be either left, right, up, or down. If your move misses, it's your opponent's turn to guess which direction you will look. The first to hit 3 moves in a row wins. 

patch notes (August 4th, 2023):
2 new finishers, Burger and Firework! I'm very sorry for lack of updates <3 working on new fun modes

data.name: Break In 2 (Story)
data.description:
A family lost with no help in sight,
rain, hail and thunder made an unpleasant night,
they took to the forest for shelter from harm,
but the tall trees above could not keep them calm,
they travelled along, their aching legs tired,
their hope for a rest had almost expired,
but there, in the distance! A wonderful find!
A building, abandoned, surely no one would mind?
They ventured forth, they knew what to do,
it was finally time for Break In 2.





Credits:

Main Building: @FRANCOJ1119
3D Models: Berkan Özkan
Main Animations: @WizardMaster29 
Other Building: @Nimb1e @RealJofu
Other Animations: @Simdiggie
Lobby Programming: @Roytt
Artwork (only the good art, if it looks like rubbish it was done by me): @Izzeke @f1zxyy 

Inspired by Camping by SamsonXVI

data.name: The Presentation Experience
data.description:

💰 Ways to earn Points include:
- Presenting: 30 Points + stars given
- Quests
- Bonus every 5 seconds
👥 Earn +1 Bonus Point for every friend you play with!
💬 Use chat to interact with the teacher!
✨ 3 second bonus interval for premium players instead of 5
💸 Private server owner earns 2x bonus Points!
💎 Use Gems to do Robux actions in 1 click!

Update 57:
👍 New action: +10 Social Credit
🔊 Fixed the sounds in actions "Give it to me" and "Cat laugh"

April Fool’s event released on April 1st!  
The event will run for about a month, therefore no need to rush to find all the limited foods.
- Added April Fool’s limited foods.
- Fixed minor bugs.
- Added global rankings for Juice Party, Hide and Seek, and Edamame Mansion.
- Added an option to hide the overhead chat of other foods.


How to Use the Private Server Functionality:
１・Join the game from a private server.
２・You can move to Hide and Seek or Small Farm maps while staying on the private server.
３・Other users can join by entering the password displayed in the bottom left of the screen.
４・You can access the password entry screen from the padlock icon in the top bar.

Sixth Annual Bloxy award winner!

The fifth Broke Bones game can be found here:

data.name: Givenchy Beauty House
data.description:
The beauty adventure begins!

Enter Givenchy castle, explore its flowery gardens and makeup your avatar with the best products of the House. The Irresistible area and the L'Interdit area, both inspired by the two emblematic fragrances of the brand, are waiting for you…

🪞 Improvise yourself as a makeup artist and enter a beauty contest
💃🏼 Show off your best dance moves on the Irresistible dancefloor
💄 Grab a lipstick Le Rouge cross-body bag at the vending machine of L'Interdit station [sold-out]
🔎 Go on a quest for the hidden 4Gs (hope you don't have vertigo...)
📸 Strike a pose in the photo booth
💦 Swim to find some surprises

Through a series of surprising games, you will be able to collect exclusive badges inspired by Givenchy beauty and fashion accessories. After winning them, we highly recommend wearing them in all Roblox experiences!

The Givenchy Beauty House, a place where beauty has no limits.

data.name: Jurassic World | TESTING BRANCH
data.description:
A fangame about... well... as the name suggests.... Jurassic World!!!!!

This project takes Jurassic World (JP aswell) and reshapes it, adding original ideas and locations, while also keeping the original ideas of the parks.
So far, you can explore the following locations: Main Street, JP (2015 and 1993), Gyrosphere Valley and Camp Cretaceous.
The game recieves yearly a big refresh of maps, ui and even dinosaurs (if there needs to be). This year was phenomenal (well, not for the dinosaurs to say the least).
There are curently 2 modes: Exploration mode and Deathmatch Mode.

The testing branch has been opened for testing!
data.sourceDescription:
A fangame about... well... as the name suggests.... Jurassic World!!!!!

This project takes Jurassic World (JP aswell) and reshapes it, adding original ideas and locations, while also keeping the original ideas of the parks.
So far, you can explore the following locations: Main Street, JP (2015 and 1993), Gyrosphere Valley and Camp Cretaceous.
The game recieves yearly a big refresh of maps, ui and even dinosaurs (if there needs to be). This year was phenomenal (well, not for the dinosaurs to say the least).
There are curently 2 modes: Exploration mode and Deathmatch Mode.

The testing branch has been opened for testing!

data.name: Vampire Life
data.description:
As a human your goal is to survive and hunt the vampires down. You are equipped with a wooden stake, you can get more weapons with your cash you get from killing vampires. Humans can get turned into vampires if they die with vampire blood in their system and then drink from a blood bag. As a vampire you need blood to survive, if you dont feed you will dessicate until someone feeds you. Vampires burn in the sunlight without daylight rings. The longer a vampire is alive the stronger they get.

Original vampires are the first vampires ever created. So they are stronger and faster than regular vamps and can compel other vampires, they can only die to the white oak stake. If an original dies every vampire they turned will also die.

data.name: H2O Mermaid Testing
data.description:
Welcome to H2O Mermaid Testing! This game is inspired by the series H2O: Just Add Water. You can choose to play as a preset character or even create your own character. If you want to see more updates, please like the game to show your support! It means a lot to me. :) 🧜‍♀️

Controls:
💧 Water: Click on the ocean to form a water bubble, then click again to throw it. Water bubbles can transform humans into mermaids.
🧊 Ice: Click on a water bubble to freeze it. If a frozen water bubble hits a player, it will damage them.
🔥 Fire: Click on a water bubble to boil it. Click on mermaids above water to dry them off.
💚 Jelly: Click on a spot on the ocean to form a jelly platform.
🌊 Dive: Run towards water and jump.

Credits:
Seagoonia: Swimming animation, faces, dive splash effects, moon pool foam effect, mermaid tops, rock and coral meshes
If you see her in game, make sure to say thank you for all of her contributions to the game!
Mattjarrett64: Cafe music

data.name: War Machines
data.description:
In this open-world sandbox experience, you can:
» Fly through the skies in powerful armored WARDEN suits.
» Unlock new suit designs and abilities.
» Fight AI or other players.

Gamepad Controls:
» A (while Mid-Air) - Fly
» LJoystick In - Sprint
» LJoystick In (while Flying) - Boost
» RT (while Boosting) - Supersonic
» RT - Shoot
» DPad Up - Eject
» Dpad Down - Toggle Mask
» Dpad Left - Toggle Rogue mode (enables pvp)
» Dpad Right - Open Event Screen

PC Controls:
» Space (while Mid-Air) - Fly
» Ctrl (while Flying) - Boost
» Left Click (while Boosting) - Supersonic
» F - Block

This game is inspired by but not affiliated with Marvel's Ironman/Avengers

data.name: Infectious Smile
data.description:
As ordinary people we all strive to find true happiness in life. But no... not like this.... something is REALLY off about this...

This game serves to remind us that life is much more complicated than finding true happiness. Sadness, struggle, and anger are a part of the human experience. If your only emotion is happiness... then.. are you really human?

For Server Owners you can use :regen & :disaster & :choosemap

laughablehaha - Scripter
yurgzen & ItsByskyWrecker - Building
sirener55 & Vinniie3D - Thumbnail & Scripting & Design

- Iron Potion duration: inf → 30 seconds
- Sign Animations: “Shy”, “High”, “Peek-a-boo”
- 2 New Maps: Isolated Mineshaft Industry, Mossy Plop Jungle

- New “Avalanche” Mountain Collapse
- Console QOL Features: DPadLeft → ShiftLock
Build and Survive

- Water Biome
- “Food Crate” Block

data.name: ESCAPE EVIL GRANDPA! (OBBY)
data.description:
Your parents have just locked you up with your crazy grandpa Eugene for the weekend. Grandpa is EVIL and absolutely HATEs his grandchildren, he won't let you run away on his watch! LET'S ESCAPE!

If you had fun playing this obby please leave a like and a favorite, it helps a lot =). Also consider joining the Decent Obbies group so that you don't miss out on future games!

⚠️ OBBY CONTAINS JUMPSCARES ⚠️

Make your way through dangerous obstacles while running from grandpa in this obby / parkour, watch out for Grandpa's MECH form!


If you're stuck on a stage make sure to check out some of the fun power-ups in the shop, any purchases are greatly appreciated and support me in making future games but don't feel pressured, simply playing the game is just as meaningful to me as a developer ❤️. Have fun!

data.name: The Intruder
data.description:
You are alone in your house. Suddenly, the phone rings. The police department issues a warning that a criminal is on the loose. Unfortunately, the criminal has a new target: YOU. Check the cameras in your room to watch his every move. He can sometimes enter your room to look for you. Hide in the closet if he does and turn off the lights. Wait until the phone regains service.

Controls:
Flashlight: [PC: F, Gamepad: Y]
Sprint (For Mineshaft): [PC: Left-Shift, Gamepad: B]
Skill-Checks: [PC: E, Gamepad: A] 
Objective: [PC: Q] 

Inspirations: The Mandela Catalogue and Five Nights at Freddy's (also a few other games)

🔺WARNING🔺: This game includes flashing lights, loud sounds, and jumpscares.

Tags: horror, scary, fnaf, intruder, cameras, monster, ghost, mandela

data.description:
basically Friday Night Funk, but again.
Make sure you play the real FNF (and its mods) if you can.

How to play: WASD or Arrow keys (can be changed in-game)

BFNF:R is FREE, Will always be FREE, and we have no intention of changing that.

Credits to MaplGalaxy and NeroBlack01 as the original creators of this game.
If there are any creators that would like their mod/song removed from the game, please reach out to one of our devs in the community server. Other ways of contact are also available.

credits to ninja_muffin99, kawaisprite, PhantomArcade3K, evilsk8r and all of the fnf mod community. I don't deserve an iota of credit.

Please make sure to report any bugs in our community server, under the Bug Reports forum.

Thumbnail art by @RayE

Have fun (and don't cheat!) :)

Welcome to Impossible Red Light, Green Light!

Race to the end with friends through the corridor of turrets, compete against foes and make your way to the cash prize jackpot! When the doll looks at you, freeze! With tools and suits inspired by Squid Game, roleplay and dress-up as your favourite character and have fun with friends. Use multiple types of accessories to customize your outfit and your avatar. Statistically speaking, you have only 1% chance to beat the obby on your first try, by yourself, meaning 99% fail! Good luck!

data.name: Trench Warfare
data.description:
Welcome to Trench Warfare, an action packed game taking place in World War I.

- 💥Fight in the Great War, one of the bloodiest wars in history!
- 🛡️ Engage in massive battles of attrition and bravery!
- 💂‍♂️ Unlock new classes and new ways to play!
- 💪 Play with friends and become the deadliest team in the trenches!
- ⚔️ Push across no man's land to victory!

Don't forget to like and favorite the game to show your support!

Expect updates in the future; new nations, new weapons, new maps, and more.

Be sure to join the group to support the developer: https://www.roblox.com/groups/10117472/J-Cowboy-Studios

Notes:
- PC controls: C - crouch, R - reload, V - melee, Shift - sprint, Ctrl - shiftlock. Mobile controls: Buttons appear when equipping tools
- Spawn points (SP) don't save, but you gain them by just being in the game
- You may need to rejoin for game passes to take effect

data.name: Color Hide and Seek
data.description:
🔥 Use code "like70k" and LIKE the game for free reward!!!
👍 NEW CODE releases once the game gets 75K LIKES!!!
🎁 Special code: "hide2023"

Seekers：Catch all players who haven't successfully hidden.
Hiders：According to the system prompt, hide next to the right color blocks.

At the beginning, one player gets chosen to be 'It'. 'It' has to try and find the other players. 'It' can run faster than everyone else, so the hiders should run near the right color blocks as quickly as possible to avoid being caught. So good luck and enjoy the game.

data.name: MR CRAZY'S CARNIVAL! (SCARY OBBY)
data.description:
It's time to enter the world's most evil carnival (run by Mr. Crazy of course). There's an entrance but there doesn't seem to be any way to leave... Hm... Is this really safe? Eh whatever, LET'S ESCAPE!

⚠️ GAME CONTAINS JUMPSCARES AND LOUD NOISES ⚠️

Can you escape Mr. Crazy and make it to stage 21 of this obby / parkour? He will be chasing you!

Finished easy mode? Try hard mode!

If you had fun playing this obby I'd be so appreciative if you were to leave a 👍 and favorite, ❤️.

If you're stuck on a stage make sure to check out some of the fun power-ups in the shop, any purchases are greatly appreciated and support me in making future games but don't feel pressured, simply playing the game is just as meaningful to me as a developer ❤️. Have fun!

Join the Decent Obbies group if you don't want to miss out on future obby games!

data.name: LAST ORDER! (SURVIVAL PUZZLE OBBY)
data.description:
So it's almost closing time at the Pizzeria and we get an order from a strange and nonsensical person!
Approaching this giant rundown house with our delivery we find that the door is Open!

We slowly enter the house to find the door locks behind us and traps us in this giant home!
Oh that's not good! We need to find a way out of here!! Can you escape this crazy house and avoid being captured by Bob?

This game is a Puzzle based survival Obby meaning we have a bit of Parkour, Puzzle Solving, and avoiding Bob who is looking for you!

Work together with your friends to figure out puzzles and ways to escape from Bob. 
This games also includes:
-A Global leader board for speed runners who like to beat games as quickly as possible
-A Capture leader board for anyone who wants to become Bob and capture your friends
-There are 6 Badges to Achieve

LAST ORDER! (SURVIVAL PUZZLE OBBY) created by SploshyGames.

data.name: School [HORROR]
data.description:
Horror game in a school.

LIKE FOR CHAPTER 3!

🧸 JOIN OUR GROUP and LIKE THE GAME 👍 for FREE TEDDY BEAR in game!: https://www.roblox.com/groups/15385098

Chapter 1: At around 2 o'clock every night in the biggest school in America, strange things happen in this school. A group of friends want to solve this mystery, but when they enter the school, they realize that the situation is much more dangerous and they do their best to escape.

Chapter 2: A group of friends travel to a private school in Ontario that has failed due to a robot experiment, and what happens to them.

Note: You can continue from where you left off by using respawn in the game.
Warning: There are things in this game that are not suitable for people with jumpscare and epilepsy.

data.name: 🔎Disguise Hunt
data.description:
Can you distinct which objects are real or just disguised hiders?🔎

Funny Hide and Seek type game, where seekers have to discover which objects and props are real and which are not. Once Hider is discovered Seekers have to chase it down ⚡️

If you are Seeker:
- Discover Hider (for mobile users double tap)
- Once Hider is discovered, chase it and catch it!
- If you can't catch the hider, just discover it 3 times and it will be automatically caught!

If you are Hider:
- Blend in the environment (for mobile users double tap)
- Taunt seekers to earn more coins
- If you got discovered - run!
- You can get discovered only 3 times!

👍 If you like the game, don't forget to leave a 👍 and follow, also join the group 😊

Bug fixes.

Welcome to Escape the Pizzeria Obby! 🍕🔥 Your mission: make a pizza and deliver it to the customer. Sounds easy, right? Wrong.

Chef Bob isn’t just cooking—he’s hunting. 😨 Dodge deadly kitchen traps, jump across sizzling ovens, and race through 26 thrilling stages to escape before you become the next topping! 🩸 Can you outsmart Chef Bob and complete your delivery, or will you end up on the menu?

💀 Run, jump, and survive—before it’s too late!

data.name: Dummies vs Noobs
data.description:
Defend Dummykind's last stronghold against the Noob hordes...

Dummies vs Noobs is a wave-based cooperative shooter that puts you in a squad of 8, against a seemingly endless horde of noobs that utilize modern and near-future weaponry. Adapt your weapons, fine tune your tactics and stay alive to see the end of the line.

WARNING: Farming EXP by manipulating or taking advantage of in-game glitches or exploits is a bannable offense. You may not use alt accounts for in-game currency either.

Controls can be viewed in keybind settings

Warrior Cats: Ultimate Edition brings the "Warriors" series off the written page and into the Roblox world!

🎨Create your own Warrior Cats, and your own story. 
🐾Choose the path of a Warrior, a Medicine Cat, or perhaps even a Clan Leader!

💬Develop friendships, alliances, and identify your foes! 
🌟Construct your own story in this immersive environment, and control your own destiny.

data.name: Worm 2048
data.description:
Welcome to Worm 2048! 

🔥 Use code "Likes50k" and LIKE the game for free reward!!!
👍 NEW CODE releases once the game gets 80000 LIKES!!!

How to Play：  
   1、 Get a bigger number by collecting free blocks and eating other players with a smaller number than you. 
   2、Your block with the same value that bump into one another will merge.(ps: you even can eat other's tail which block is smaller than your head size)
   3、Use accelerated power to escape who bigger than you!

Have Fun and Enjoy the game!!!!!

data.name: 🌍NEW MAPS🔥 Don't leave the circle!⭕️
data.description:
💣This is a survival game.💣 
To win, you need to be the last one standing inside the red circle. 
To survive, you have to keep track of your statistics: Food, Water, Toilet and Sleep. 
The players are provided with food and one cup of water every day. At night, everyone is given sleeping bags in which you can restore your sleep. There are bonus games every day, which might be a parkour obby, tower, football and much more!

 NEW MINIGAMES:
- Red light Green Light, squid game
- Gas attack
- Disco dance
- Tsunami 
- Lazer masks
- Lazer jump
- Falling supports
- Dodgeball

 NEW MAPS
-Island
-Concrete pillar

data.name: Ultimate Ragdoll Playground
data.description:
[New] Slow Motion Tool!

You've played ragdoll games before, but none quite come close to Ultimate Ragdoll Playground! If you enjoy watching your Roblox avatar ragdolling then you've come to the right place! 

Play now for unique features including: 
- Aimable cannons 🎉 
- Throwable bombs, mines, and boomerangs 💣🪃 
- Pipes you can travel through 🔧 
- Giant boombox with bouncy speakers 📾 
- A rocket you can grab onto and go to space 🚀 
- Giant tornado! 🌪️ 
- Train 🚂 
- Paraglider 🪂 
- UFO 🛸

Along with the traditional stairs, slides, tower block, balloons and more!

- R - Ragdoll 
- F - Toggle gravity 
- C - Toggle first person view

productInfo.Name: Escape Bob the Dentist! SCARY OBBY

data.name: Escape Bob the Dentist! SCARY OBBY
data.description:
If you have fun please thumbs-up 👍 and favorite ⭐ to support the game. Thank you so much for playing!

It's the year 2150 and all dentists have gone out of business due to the recent invention of invincible dentures, except Bob. You weren't able to get your hands on this new invention and so therefore you've been forced to go to Bob to have your teeth cleaned. But Bob has gone a little crazy in recent years and decides to trap you inside the building, MUHAHAHA!!! THERE'S NO ESCAPING NOW!!!

Can you beat all 23 stages of this obby / parkour and make it to safety?

If you're stuck on a stage make sure to check out some of the power-ups in the shop, any purchases are greatly appreciated and support me in making future games but don't feel pressured, simply playing the game is just as meaningful to me as a developer ❤️. Have fun!

data.description:
Super Bomb Survival is a physics-based survival game where it's raining explosives from the sky! Join your friends & enemies alike in this frantic scramble to avoid explosions of all kinds! Battle, escape random events, and become a badge tycoon! 

Buy over 60 Skills & over 20 Perks at the game's Survival Shop to tailor your character to your play-style, or hang out in the arcade and goof off. You can even ragdoll at any time!

If you enjoy the game, leave a like/favorite! It helps a lot!

Logo by tanukizzy

data.name: Da Hood
data.description:
A difficult game, read below for tips. 
Account has to be at least 10 days to play. 

You can weave 100% if you time at the right time when blocking. To gain muscle buy weights at fitness. 
Eat lettuce to reduce muscle.

Cop: To join cops go to the police station, if you execute anyone without cuffs you'll be automatically kicked off. Use cuffs instead. 
Criminals: Ransack banks and several others small time shops in order to gain wanted or cash. 

Gun saves - however, can be lost by death, or logging when KO, or 0 ammo. 

Cash drop takes 30%

You'll never look at cartoons the same way again.

data.name: Curse Battlegrounds
data.description:
U can switch characters at the top left of your screen, there's a character icon.

Like the game for more updates & characters

You can play on any device. (CONSOLE, PC, MOBILE)
game is in development, so expect bugs

CONTROLS:
M1 - Attack
F - Block
Q - Dash
Q (while ragdolled) - Ragdoll Cancel / Evasive
W + W - Run
G - Awakening / Ultimate

B - Emote Wheel

[most of everything in the game is made by p4k, this is a solo project, updates WILL be slow]

A cool battlegrounds game based on the series JJK.
Inspired by TSB

data.name: Southwest Florida Beta
data.description:
⚠️ All forms of exploiting, including exploiting your car, will result in a PERMENANT ban. Bear this in mind! ⚠️

Welcome to Southwest Florida! Based around the Bonita Springs area, Southwest Florida is a roleplay game that offers a variety of jobs, vehicles, and more! 

⚠️ This game is not complete and some features are missing.

⚠️ This is a large game and lower end PCs, laptops, phones, and tablets may experience performance issues.

Controls
- "V" to toggle walk/jog, hold "Shift" to run
- Semi & Auto: "E" to upshift, "Q" to downshift ("X" and "Y" on Xbox)
- Manual: Use the "Shift" key ("RB" on Xbox) to control clutch while shifting
- Hold left-CTRL while accelerating to wheelie on a bike

⚠️ If you have seen anyone breaking Roblox's Community Standards, please submit a report by interacting with the player list and vote-kick that person.

Shortcuts: 
CTRL+Scroll / [ ] - increase/decrease paint thickness
Shift+P - toggle freecam
Numbers 1-4 - Tool Selection

You can hide/votekick/report other players by interacting with the player list.

Note: It can take up to a week to receive Robux from any doodle sales!

Join the group for an extra +500 ink limit! Like the game if you enjoyed drawing doodles! 👍

data.name: Push Dummies Down The Sparta Hole!
data.description:
THIS! IS SPARTA!!!!!!
Dedicated to giving new Robloxians a classic Roblox game experience!

Duel over the hole with swords and fight to the death! Use the noob tube! Drive cars to the bottom and watch them explode! Ragdoll down the pit! Skydive to the bottom and reach where only the strongest players reside! And of course... PUSH DUMMIES DOWN THE SPARTA HOLE! 

Thank you all for playing over the years! Many of you have told me that this game is a part of your childhood, I'm very grateful to all of you that have played! You're all the reason I keep this game updated and working! :D

[VOICE ENABLED]

Credits:
Sethers10 - Game Creator

Rile_ey - Scripting

data.name: Escape Mr Funny's ToyShop! (SCARY OBBY)
data.description:
So its your first day as a Security guard for Mr Funny's ToyShop. 
Its your job to make sure no one robs the place, Also.. It's important to keep the power OFF! The factory seems to encounter....Problems?...When the Power is turned on during the Night shift. 
Just sit back, Relax and make sure not to turn on the power BUT..
Lets say you do turn it on and need to escape well, 
Travel through the 20 crazy Obstacles and mini games that await you. 
Make your way through the Factory and make sure to avoid the Mr Funny Dummy that lurks in the darkness. 

Thank you all for playing games and I really hope you enjoy them. I try to keep my games new and fresh to keep you all entertained :)
Please help out and leave a Like and Favorite :)

Credits to MaxXD_22 for making "NEED MORE HEAT." This game were heavily inspired by it. Go play his game if you haven't yet!

data.name: Among Us RP
data.description:
drip!
Step into the world of Among Us Roleplay, where the tension runs high and the stakes are even higher! In this roleplay game, players assume the roles of crew members aboard a spacecraft, working diligently to complete tasks and maintain the ship's integrity. However, lurking among them are impostors with nefarious intentions.

One of the key mechanics is the ability to 'Vent.' Impostors can use the ship's ventilation system to move quickly and stealthily between rooms, enabling them to strike unsuspecting crew members and sabotage their efforts. Venting adds a new layer of strategy to the game, as impostors must choose when and where to vent carefully to avoid detection.

data.name: Animal Life: Forest RP🐺🐴 🦌🦝🐰
data.description:
Explore this animal world and roleplay as a horse, wolf, bear, moose, rabbit, fox, raccoon, red panda, deer, cougar, leopard, or raven!

Report bugs on the group wall (Humongous).

Free private servers available for dedicated roleplay or anything.

Controls:
Change your animal: Click the fox head icon to go to the customization panel. Then click the 2 animal head icon on the top to go to the animal selection panel.

Change your colors: Click the fox head icon to go to the customization panel. It should already be on the color panel, so click on simple colors for a list of preset colors for different areas of the animal, or click advanced colors to color specific parts custom colors.

Double jump to fly.

The basis of the models and animations are by MalberS Animations.

data.name: Team School Escape! (TEAMWORK OBBY)
data.description:
If you have fun please thumbs-up 👍 and favorite ⭐ to support the game. Thank you so much for playing!

(Private servers are free!)

It's time to escape school! Are you prepared for what awaits?
Our teacher has been keeping us in detention for what feels like FOREVER and it is starting to make us ANGRY 😡!!! Although he spends most of his time sleeping he is NOT going to make it easy for us to leave! Let's work together to escape from this place before he catches us!!!

If you're stuck on a stage make sure to check out some of the fun power-ups in the shop, any purchases are greatly appreciated and support me in making future games but don't feel pressured, simply playing the game is just as meaningful to me as a developer ❤️. Have fun!

Join the Decent Obbies group so you don't miss out on future obby / parkour games!

data.name: Saiyan Battlegrounds
data.description:
Fight against everyone to become the best Z warrior

🌐 ✨ You can play on any device: console, PC, or mobile. Now supported on all platforms!

⭐ If you enjoy it, give it a like and add to favorites to encourage more frequent updates!

🎮 Controls:

Left-click: Execute powerful strikes with unstoppable ferocity to vanquish your enemies.

Q + movement keys: Execute agile and evasive maneuvers with a dash in your chosen direction, liberating yourself from your character's ragdoll state every 15 seconds. Master the art of swift and strategic movements.

F: Use the block function to shield against enemy attacks. Choose when to deploy for maximum effectiveness.

G: Unleash extraordinary abilities with your ultimate attack. Ensure your ability bar is charged for maximum impact. Turn the tide of battle with your ultimate ability.

Recognitions ✨:
Game inspired by the Dragon Ball series and The Strongest Battlegrounds game

data.name: [V2.17] Ghost at the Door
data.description:
🎉Update 2.17🎉
🔖Added more level tag styles.
🎮Added a "play again" feature.
❤️Optimized interaction for fear value, pets, and prop systems.
🔧Fixed several known bugs.

Can you survive if a ghost is crazily trying to break into your house at midnight?
It's important to choose a room with essential equipment before the ghost shows up to help you survive, such as lavender, a safe, and a toolbox.
Remember, the key to winning is to upgrade your door as soon as possible or to kill the ghost before it becomes strong enough to demolish your door.
Upgrade door and artillery needs sufficient resources, whice requires a strategy to obtain and then balance them.

If you find the game difficult to play, you can try learning from other players.

If you enjoy this game, please give us a like👍
🔔Favorite our game to get more updates!🔔

Bare in mind you are also getting chased by Papa Pizza Himself!!

data.name: Princess Tycoon
data.description:
Welcome to Princess Tycoon 😄, choose your favorite princess 👸 and build 🧱 your tycoon! 

You purchase droppers 🏗️ that generate cash 💸, when you have enough cash you will be able to unlock different weapons ⚔️ of your chosen princess and unlock the princess outfit 👗.

The objective of the game is to unlock all weapons 🗡️ of the chosen princess and the princess outfit inside your tycoon 👑! Fight others to defend your tycoon and become the most powerful princess ✨ in the game! Make sure to invite or make friends 👥 along the way that can help you build your tycoon and fight others 👊!

Join The Tycoon Squad ✌️ for 2,500 starting cash 💰:
https://www.roblox.com/groups/group.aspx?gid=4965451
In the group, you can also find our other tycoon games 🎮, and you can chat with the community 👪. Make sure to post about your game/update ideas 🤔 on our group wall!

Make sure to favorite ⭐ and thumbs up 👍 the game to show your support!

data.name: Every Second You Get Older  [🎉100M🎉]
data.description:
This is a thrilling Roblox game that puts your skills to the test as you 👶👦👧 get older every second. As the ⏰ ticks, your avatar grows older, and you must complete challenges to earn wins🏆 and progress through the game.

⚙️UPDATE⚙️
- Codes ⚙️
- Wheel of fortune 🍀
- Effect auto seller ♻️
- 2 New ages 👦
- Better UI 🎮
- Bug Fixes 🐛

Codes: THANKYOUFOR100M
Next free code for 30K likes 🏆

The challenges are designed to test your  skill🏃‍♂️🧠. Each challenge completed successfully earns you  wins🏆.

But that's not all - once you reach a certain year 🎂, you can perform a rebirth ♻️, which resets your avatar's year to zero and gives you a fresh start. Rebirths also give you special perks and bonuses that help you progress faster through the game.

Can you reach the highest year 🏅 and become the ultimate champion? Play now and find out! 🎮

data.name: Build A Boat With Blocks
data.description:
👋 Welcome to Build A Boat With Blocks! 👋

⚠️ PLEASE NOTE ⚠️
This game is inspired by the popular game "Build A Boat For Treasure." Credit goes to them for the original game idea! Please show your support for their game too! 😄

❓How To Play❓
Build a boat and set sail! The farther you go, the more cash you earn! Buy blocks and build bigger boats. Your progress is automatically saved!

💾 Latest Updates! 💾

v1.37.0

-Added Inventory Sharing Mode
-Updated the game's datastore
-Nerfed the snowflake obstacle
-Tons of bug fixes and other smaller additions 

v1.36.0

-Halloween update with new limited items
-Increased build height
-You can now press 'Tab' to toggle the player board
-It now shows which player launched your team's boat
-Loads of bug fixes and smaller additions

Development Group:
https://www.roblox.com/groups/11606484

data.name: SCP: Roleplay
data.description:
Welcome to SCP: Roleplay!

In this world, terrifying or unusual creatures and objects called SCPs roam the earth.
To protect humanity from them, the SCP Foundation was created.
The Foundation conducts experiments to learn more about the SCPs.
The mission of the Foundation is to secure, contain and protect the SCPs.

Play as a Prisoner (Class - D), Scientist, Guard, and unlock more teams as you progress.

Will you assist them or will you bring chaos to the world?

[!] It is important that you read the rules: 
https://devforum.roblox.com/t/scp-roleplay-game-rules/
(Licensing Attributions are also above on the rules post)

[NOTE] To access different modes such as Infection, you can use the Modes button on the right side of the menu.

data.description:
🎉Code "2KLIKES" and "5KLIKES" for Free Gift🎉

🚀 Hide and Seek Mode Rules🚀
Hide and Seek Mode Rules:
1 or 2 Impostor each round and everybody knows who he/she is.
Innocent got time to run away from impostor at the beginning.
No found body report, No emergency meeting.
Impostor and Innocent can turn on/off light to hide or seek.
Impostor Win: Kill all Innocents
Innocent Win: All innocent complete tasks or time's up 
If you are a ghost, also can help to complete the tasks.

Control:
Impostor Use "E" or "R1"(Console) to kill

🔧 This game is in BETA joins the communications server to stay updated and report bugs.
👍 Leave a thumbs up if you enjoy it, we are providing more content and updates for you.
☁️ Inspired by Among Us and Hide And Seek.

data.name: [Portal Update] Secret Neighbor [BETA]
data.description:
Secret Neighbor, a multiplayer social horror game that challenges you to uncover the secrets hidden in your neighbor's infamous house, NOW on ROBLOX.

QoL#1 Changes: 

🏁 Jump in the PORTALS to start your fav game mode

🕵️ Keep an eye out for a hint where the basement door is; watch out, it lasts only 20 seconds! 

🔓 Count the remaining locks right on your screen!

🙅 Neighbors won’t change in the beginning of the match anymore (yes, we’re looking at you ‘early’ catchers 🦹‍♂️)

🧰 Many other fixes and under-the-hood improvements

🐷Unlock exclusive content in Piggy Build Mode by earning the coveted "Welcome to the Neighborhood" badge!

___________

👋TEAMWORK
Team-up and UNLOCK the basement door. Sticking together is THE key to success!

🤫Unmask THE traitor
Look-around and BEWARE of the masked NEIGHBOR! 👀 

🧐Outsmart the Neighbor
Don’t let The Neighbor brag with the win!

🎃Dress for the occasion
With Neighbor Skins or Rescue Squad Costumes, it’s your time to shine ✨

data.name: Image Block Run
data.description:
Challenge your friends to a fun image race in Image Block Run!

How to play:
1. Run to the finish line without falling.

data.name: Wings of Fire [Beta]
data.description:
Roleplay in the world of Wings of Fire!

Wings of Fire is a series of fantasy novels, taking place on the two fictional, dragon-inhabited continents of Pyrrhia and Pantala. Each novel takes you on a thrilling adventure of various twists and turns, following a lovable cast of dragonets attempting to save their world from war! 

The game is a fan project dedicated to all the fans of our favourite book series and it's lovely author.

Expect shutdowns and data wipes for updates/bug fixes.
Planned additions: scavengers, more quests, accessories, maps, and more!

data.name: Tsunami Game
data.description:
Combine "Squid Game Red Light Green Light" with "Be Crushed By A Speeding Wall" Add Tsunami 🌊

Survive tsunamis to get to the other side.  
A button anyone can press controls when a tsunami will spawn, and the longer that button is left alone, the larger the tsunami will be.
As you cross the game, you will gain Risk and collect Points. 
Use earned Points to purchase gear items to better prepare for future crossings. 
As you progress you'll begin to uncover secrets and realize there is more than meets the eye.

Roblox Premium users gains 25% more Risk

data.name: Altitorture [2 Player Obby]
data.description:
⚠️ This game is made for 2 players, to get the best experience play with a friend. ⚠️

Climb your way out of a deep pit with your friend in this obby game. The pit is unforgiving and the climb is tough, but you’re not alone. You and your friend are attached via an elastic rope that will test your teamwork and coordination. Learn how to use the rope to your advantage and overcome the challenges of being dependent on each other. Can you make it to the top?

How to start:
 - Go up to someone you'd like to pair up with.
 - Press the "Request rope" button.
 - To accept a request simply go up a requesting person and request a rope back.
 - You're set, have fun!

⛰️ Current maximum altitude: 500 M

Developer credits: Maxiimized [Building | Scripting], R0T1CAL [Building | Scripting], FlowingHourglass [Building]

data.name: Alo Sanctuary
data.description:
MOVE INTO WELLNESS WITH ALO

Explore the Alo Sanctuary through Movement, Mindfulness, and Recovery.

Lace up your Alo Runner sneakers and power through 3, 5, and 7-minute guided runs while exploring motivational touch points in multi-terrain environments.

Spend your rest day in the Make Waves set and Recovery Mode Sneakers, designed for the ultimate post-workout relaxation.

Cool off in a refreshing ice bath, take a dip in a serene infinity pool, or recenter with a calming meditation.

Elevate your wellness journey in the Alo Sanctuary for a daily retreat full of exclusive rewards. 

NEW FREE LIMITED ALO UGC ITEMS ARE HERE!
Claim your exclusive UGC items by participating in challenges and logging in consecutively for 3, 7 and 10 days. New (Free) UGC releasing every 2 weeks!

data.name: strict brother [SHOP]
data.description:
You arrive home after a long day, excited to play some video games. You find out your older brother is now in charge of the house. This cant be that bad right..?

Death is apart of the experience! Learn from your deaths in order to achieve your goal.

PC Controls:
LShift to Sprint
C to Tiptoe
E to Interact
X for Secondary Interact
V to Unlock Mouse
Q to Dodge

XBOX Controls:
L2 to Sprint
Y to Tiptoe
X to Interact
B for Secondary Interact
Y to Dodge

Mobile/PC/XBOX Support

Inspired by weird strict dad

data.name: 🔥NEED MORE HEAT🔥
data.description:
Oh no, it's Monday o'clock! Yuck! You really don't wanna go to school, do you?
Hm... I know! Try to convice your strict dad that you have a fever!

Turns out that won't be as easy as it seems and you'll end up desperately trying to increase the temperature as much as possible.

This game was inspired by similar funny games, such as "do your homework at 3AM", "be a dad and get milk simulator", or "buy food to feed your cat". Although this game has 7 distinct endings, it has a more linear gameplay style than those.

data.name: Nightlight [HORROR]
data.description:
Welcome to Nightlight [HORROR]!

【 About 】
Lost in a forest in the dead of night, you seek out refuge in a friendly stranger's home, but something feels off. You must atone for your past greed. Collect 8 notes spelling out "Selfish." to break free. Stay vigilant, your candle is your lifeline.

This game can be difficult for new players, do not be upset if you don't beat it the first try.

【 Recommendations】
⚠️ At least 60% graphics recommended
🤝 Joining with other players can be used to your advantage
🔥 Protect your candle's flame by finding hidden matches
🎧 Headphones recommended

❗ Join the group and community
🛠️ Game is still in early testing. Many things could change. Please report bugs.

Tags: Horror, Night, Dark, Light, Scary, Night Light, Midnight

data.name: 👑STRONGEST PUNCH SIMULATOR
data.description:
Are you ready to become the strongest of them all?

GUIDE
Break Through Walls --> Reach World Borders --> Teleport To Higher Worlds --> - Collect Power Ups Hidden Behind The Walls --> Feed Your Mythical Pets And Evolve Them --> Become Stronger --> Do You Desire To Protect Or Destroy, Take Your Sides!

FAQ
- Experiencing lag? Turn on ‘Fast Mode’ in settings
- Punch terrain walls to gain double the amount of power!
- Become stronger to create bigger punch explosions!
- Train in higher worlds to gain more power!
- Higher worlds have denser terrains causing your area of explosion to be reduced!
- Upgrade Punch Multiplier to train faster!
- Damage done to stronger heroes will reflect back upon yourself!
- Choose to attack only good/bad heroes in settings to prevent unwanted reputation losses!

In this game, you'll have the opportunity to purchase a wide range of guns, cars, clothes and more stuff, giving you the power to dominate the streets. data.name: Inadequate Mod
data.description:
Game is being entirely overhauled, please be patient :D.

This game is based on another really cool game called Garry's Mod, basically a Gmod wanna-be. Just get the actual game if you can afford it, it's better.

This game is a Sandbox game where you can do whatever you want. You can destroy things, have NPC battles, become an NPC, or make environments with props,  you could also explore. Items with a shield icon mean they can only be accessed if you made the server or have someone enable it in their server.

Basic Controls
-Mouse wheel to select between items.
-P to open settings. you can change binds here
-Q to open the spawn menu
-L to open the admin panel, you can only do this as a server admin or owner.
-E to sit down or interact with an object

Physics Gun Controls
-Mouse wheel to move forwards or backward
-Hold your interact key (E by default) to activate rotation mode. Move your mouse to then rotate.
-Right-click to freeze.

data.description:
[NEW!]
Welcome to Five Nights at Freddy's [Story] A group of 2-6 friends are hired to be security guards at Freddy Fazbear's Pizza where strange things start to happen. It's up to you and your friends to survive for 5 nights!

Credit: Scott Cawthon ♡

🎁 Join the Mousetrap Studios group for free in-game Rewards! 🎁

🛒 Struggling to survive? Check out the store for some helpful perks to help you survive! 🛒

This game is inspired by the Five Nights at Freddy's movie, but is not exactly like it.

data.name: 🎆🍣 Conveyor Sushi Restaurant
data.description:
Welcome to Ocean Sushi! Invite your friends, eat sushi from the conveyor belt, and place orders with the order screen!

👍 Like the game for updates!

🎮 How to Eat Sushi:
1. Find a table and sit down
2. Grab sushi from the conveyor or order food and drinks from the Order Screen!
3. Put the food down on the table and eat with chopsticks!
4. Earn sushi, explore the city, open prize capsules, and have fun with your friends.

📈 UPDATE 28:
- 🎁 ADVENT CALENDAR! Come back daily for a new reward until the 24th!
- 🥢SEASONAL chopstick capsule: Winter Chopsticks!
- 🎄 MAP decorations & limited-time foods!

data.name: [ORIGINS] Michael's Zombies
data.description:
Michael was displeased with you and placed you inside his Zombies pocket dimension. Will you be able to survive his wrath? Fight against endless waves of zombies alone or with friends!

Private servers allow you to play all previously available event maps and give admin commands!

Version 2.0.0:
Added our second most requested map, Origins!
Full easter egg and buyable ending!
Applied some patches to the interaction system.

Controls: 
Interact - [F] / [Button X]
Shoot - [Left Mouse] / [Right Trigger]
Reload - [R] / [Controller X]
Aim Down Sights - [Q] / [Right Mouse] / [Left Bumper]
Swap Weapons - [1], [2], [3], [Scroll Wheel] / [Button Y]
Sprint - [Left Shift] / [Left Joystick Button]
Crouch / Slide - [C] / [Left Control] / [Button B]
Knife - [V] / [Right Joystick Button]
Grenades - [G] / [Right Bumper]
Settings - [P] / [DPad Left]
Leaderboard [Tab] / [DPad Right]

data.name: Goddess Tycoon 🔱😇
data.description:
Welcome to Goddess Tycoon🔱😇, choose your favorite goddess 👩 and build 🏠 your tycoon! 
 
You buy droppers 🏗️ that generate cash 💵, when you have enough cash you will be able to unlock different weapons 🔫 of your chosen goddess and unlock the goddess outfit 🔱.
 
The objective of the game is to unlock all weapons 🗡️ of the chosen goddess and the goddess outfit inside your tycoon 🏛️! Fight others to defend your tycoon and become the most powerful goddess ✨ in the game! Make sure to invite or make friends 💕 along the way that can help you build your tycoon and fight others 🏆!
 
Join Our Group ✌️ for an IN-GAME chat tag 💬:
https://www.roblox.com/groups/group.aspx?gid=11010605
Don't forget to leave your suggestions ❓ on our group wall!
 
Make sure to favorite ⭐ and thumbs up 👍 the game to show your support!

data.name: Goddess Tycoon
data.description:
Welcome to Goddess Tycoon 😄, choose your favorite goddess 🧝‍♀️ and build 🧱 your tycoon! 
 
You purchase droppers 🏗️ that generate cash 💸, when you have enough cash you will be able to unlock different weapons ⚔️ of your chosen goddess and unlock the goddess outfit 🔱.
 
The objective of the game is to unlock all weapons 🗡️ of the chosen goddess and the goddess outfit inside your tycoon 🏛️! Fight others to defend your tycoon and become the most powerful goddess 🌟 in the game! Make sure to invite or make friends 👥 along the way that can help you build your tycoon and fight others 👊!
 
Join The Tycoon Squad ✌️ for 2,500 starting cash 💰:
https://www.roblox.com/groups/group.aspx?gid=4965451
In the group, you can also find our other tycoon games 🎮, and you can chat with the community 👪. Make sure to post about your game/update ideas 🤔 on our group wall!
 
Make sure to favorite ⭐ and thumbs up 👍 the game to show your support!

data.name: 🧊 NEED MORE COLD 🧊
data.description:
It's a Friday morning and Ariana Grande is having a concert at school! You really wanna go, but you have a fever and you're burning with heat. Try to convince your weird strict mom that you aren't sick so you can go to school!

There is a problem though. Your strict mother doesn't let you go so easily, and you have to struggle past multiple tasks to decrease your temperature. YOU NEED MORE COLD!

All credit goes to MaxXD_22 for making "NEED MORE HEAT" for inspiring this game and this more linear type of ending games. This game wouldn't exist without the creation of his game so play his game if you haven't already.

Play my other game: "go to school at 3 am", in my profile. It was inspired by 'buying food to feed your cat' by Jimmalonia, ”go poop at 3 am”, ”get divorced at 3 am”, ”get a drink at 3 am”, ”get a snack at 4 am”

Tags: Endings, Need More Cold, Strict

data.description:

-Update
[+] Added level 6 - the final stage for a true escape from this infinite, abandoned hotel
[+] Added Skin items - If you purchased "Floating Ofuda", "Lantern" before, please come to our community.

data.name: The Long Drive
data.description:
📄The Long Drive is an adventure racing simulator with an apocalyptic theme and elements of survival in the harsh conditions of the surrounding world.

📄E - Interaction.
📄Shift - Run.
📄F - Use headlights.
📄R - Reload.
📄Backspace - Throw away an item.
📄V - Release the mouse.
📄Q - Turn on the music.
📄H - Honk.
📄X - Turn signals.

💎The peculiarity of the game is that the world can change completely randomly, which will not allow you to anticipate or avoid a dangerous situation.

✅Avoid the Svintusov and get to Almaty with loot boxes!

📊You should always be prepared for unexpected turns of events, strive to develop the main character, and also not forget about the main means of transportation.

📝Many features were taken from the original The Long Drive game, but we tried to change most of the mechanics.

data.name: Hold People: The Game [Voice Chat]
data.description:
Notice: Voice Chat needs to be enabled in settings to be able to use voice chat.

A game where you hold people and throw them off the map.

The longer in the game you stay the more time you get. You can use time to buy things in the shop basically they act like coins. There is also an obby you can earn time from completing. There are also many secrets around the map, like a cave, a sword and even lava! Another thing you could also do is pick up people and do weird things with them like throwing them off the map and hurting them in other ways. If you want to you can also decorate a house using things in the map!

Pc Hold: E
Mobile Hold: Button

This game is playable in singeplayer and multiplayer. The genres present in the game are Obby, Adventure, Decorating, Battle and Glitches or using bugs, Voice Chat

data.name: Flee the Facility [DUPLO]
data.description:
Basically a different version of Flee the Facility with badges, beast powers, and more.

Updates [3/1/24] 
- Added new hammers and gems. 
- Carried over the preference to keep music muted to the trading post. 
- Also made it to where when you select "TRADING OFF" in the trading post, it will stay off when you rejoin the game. 
- Made it to where you won't get up while crawling if there is something above you. 
- Added more checks to the hit detection system to decrease the likelihood of air hits. 
- Added a new menu where you can view the credits for players who've contributed to the game. 
- Added one new achievement: Master Hacker. Unlock by hacking five computers in one round! 
- Cosmetic changes to the Farmland map. 
- Small changes to the Facility map.

[4/15/24]
- Fixed an issue where the "Return" button wouldn't work in the map observation area.

data.name: I Wanna Test The Game (Beta Test)
data.description:
⚠ THIS GAME IS A BETA TEST, THERE WILL BE BUGS! ⚠

This is only a beta test (yes, I had to say it twice) of the first world for "I Wanna Be The Bloxxer", which is based on a game called "I Wanna Be The Guy". This is NOT the full game, as it is still being developed (which is why some elements in the stage DON'T work). People who disliked = Stinky noobs who can't git gud. 

---CONTROLS--- 
Double press jump to double jump 
Press R or 'Retry' button to retry 
Press Z Or Crouch to save in a save station 
Crouch right before you get hit to perform a parry 

Press Q and E to equip/unequip (used for enemies, mini bosses and boss fights) Supported Platform: PC Mobile Console

data.name: Flicker 💡
data.description:
flick... flick...
When the lights go out, the murderer strikes.

Flicker is a social deduction game where you must use clues and intuition to eliminate your enemies. Everyone has a hidden ability, but not everyone may be telling the truth about what theirs is. Interrogate suspects, tell fates, protect others, point fingers, help the killer evade capture... or be the killer everyone is searching for.

RULES: https://devforum.roblox.com/t/348086
UPDATE LOG: https://devforum.roblox.com/t/1188352
CREDITS: https://devforum.roblox.com/t/717693

Created by JJ Studios 🔪

data.name: Welcome to Bloxburg
data.description:
👋 QUACK! Welcome to the wonderful waddling town of Bloxburg, where you can live your best duck life!
 
🏡 Build the perfect nest, decorate it with style, or claim the ultimate duck pond!
🦆 Dress your feathers in fancy outfits and take on fun roles—perhaps a professional bread collector?
🎭 Roleplay with your flock using interactive items and the finest honks and flaps!
💼 Find a job, earn shiny coins, and treat yourself to an endless buffet of breadcrumbs!
🚗 Hop into a vehicle (or just paddle gracefully) and explore every corner of town!
🏆 Level up your ducky skills, like cooking delicious snacks (extra grain, please), and unlock exciting content!

Thanks for playing! Make sure to follow us ⭐ and give the game a thumbs up! 👍 

Genres: Roleplay, Building, Life Simulation, Hangout, Town & City, Driving

data.name: [🎪DIGITAL CIRCUS] BARRY'S PRISON RUN! (Obby)
data.description:
⚡️SHUT DOWN = GLOBAL UPDATE/FIX⚡️

Are you ready to break out of Prison?! Well let's do this!
Today is Paradise Baby Barry's Shift and he isn't exactly the most vigilant guard in the Prison. This gives us more of an advantage to make our escape.
